# 🎓 AI-Powered Admission Counselor

An intelligent admission counseling assistant powered by Large Language Models (LLMs) and integrated with APIs to help students explore the best-fit courses and universities based on their preferences, academic background, and real-time data.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔍 **Student Profiling:** Accepts user inputs such as interests, marks, preferred location, and stream.
- 🤖 **LLM-based Recommendation:** Uses advanced LLMs to analyze data and provide personalized university/course suggestions.
- 🌐 **Real-Time Data Fetching:** Integrates with web scraping tools (e.g., BeautifulSoup) or public APIs for live university/course information.
- 📊 **SWOT Analysis:** Evaluates student strengths and weaknesses to guide career path decisions.
- 📈 **Interactive Chat:** Provides conversational, step-by-step counseling experience.
- 🛠️ **Modular Design:** Clean and well-documented codebase for easy customization and scalability.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Python 3.10+**
- **OpenAI API** – for language generation and decision-making
- **BeautifulSoup4** – for scraping university/course data (if API not available)
- **Pandas & NumPy** – for data handling and processing
- **Scikit-learn (optional)** – for clustering or decision logic
- **Streamlit (optional)** – to deploy as a web-based counselor UI

---

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/admission-counselor-llm.git
cd admission-counselor-llm
pip install -r requirements.txt
